more time with you, Starbuck.

4
00:00:33,450 --> 00:00:35,665
We have a lot to talk about !
It's gonna be fun.

5
00:00:36,883 --> 00:00:38,622
Congratulations, Commander.

6
00:00:38,703 --> 00:00:41,416
The Pegasus is your command.

7
00:00:44,097 --> 00:00:46,438
I am picking up a large planetary body.

8
00:00:46,570 --> 00:00:48,119
It's habitable.

9
00:00:48,167 --> 00:00:50,717
We may have just found a world
that can support human life.

10
00:00:50,900 --> 00:00:55,180
I know in my gut that settling on this
planet's gonna mean disaster for humanity,

11
00:00:55,222 --> 00:00:58,008
and I will not say otherwise
just to win an election.

12
00:00:58,073 --> 00:01:00,978
I take the office of president
of the twelve Colonies of Kobol

13
00:01:01,020 --> 00:01:03,438
and I'm going
to sign my first executive order.

14
00:01:03,480 --> 00:01:06,066
Requiring to immediately
establish settlements

15
00:01:06,108 --> 00:01:08,318
on the planet we have come to know

16
00:01:08,569 --> 00:01:10,028
as New Caprica.

17
00:01:10,070 --> 00:01:12,531
If you want to move down there, go ahead.
Be my guest.

18
00:01:12,573 --> 00:01:14,908
Go down and cat around with all the men.

19
00:01:14,950 --> 00:01:17,405
Saul, I want you.

20
00:01:17,471 --> 00:01:20,330
<i>At last, a safe haven we can call home.</i>

21
00:01:24,973 --> 00:01:26,676
Oh, my Gods.

22
00:01:26,954 --> 00:01:29,756
It's a cylon fleet, they found us.

23
00:01:29,798 --> 00:01:31,258
<i>We have to get out of here, sir.</i>

24
00:01:31,300 --> 00:01:33,302
We can't just leave all those people behind.

25
00:01:33,343 --> 00:01:34,761
There's nothing we can do.

26
00:01:34,803 --> 00:01:36,388
<i>We're in no shape for a fight, sir.</i>

27
00:01:36,430 --> 00:01:39,096
<i>- They'll be wiped out.
- We don't have a choice.</i>

28
00:01:39,181 --> 00:01:41,612
<i>We need to get out of here right now !</i>

29
00:01:41,669 --> 00:01:43,812
<i>Begin jump prep. We're leaving.

30
00:01:45,124 --> 00:01:46,273
But we'll be back.

31
00:01:46,315 --> 00:01:49,610
Cylons just jumped into orbit
and the fleet's jumped away.

32
00:01:49,666 --> 00:01:51,206
They've left us.

33
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:53,989
On behalf of the people of
the twelve Colonies...

34
00:01:56,081 --> 00:01:57,226
I surrender.

35
