{\a6}Yes.

50
00:06:45,794 --> 00:06:47,074
{\a6}Yes.

51
00:06:48,343 --> 00:06:50,327
Come on !
Don't stop.

52
00:06:50,744 --> 00:06:51,952
Come on !

53
00:06:52,018 --> 00:06:53,360
Come on !

54
00:06:53,426 --> 00:06:56,666
{\a6}You son of a bitch ! Son of a bitch !

55
00:07:01,716 --> 00:07:02,777
Baby !

56
00:07:12,557 --> 00:07:14,313
{\a6}Oh, boy.

57
00:07:23,443 --> 00:07:25,279
All right, we're armed.

58
00:07:27,563 --> 00:07:29,157
They're inbound. Let's move !

59
