I need a knife.

60
00:08:12,125 --> 00:08:13,410
Thank you.

61
00:08:17,412 --> 00:08:18,832
You're welcome.

62
00:08:28,011 --> 00:08:31,136
I must say I quite enjoyed that.

63
00:08:32,538 --> 00:08:34,264
{\a6}I'm so glad.

64
00:08:37,815 --> 00:08:39,684
And...

65
00:08:39,806 --> 00:08:41,772
when do I get what I want ?

66
00:08:42,704 --> 00:08:45,651
I believe that's happening right now.

67
00:08:56,377 --> 00:08:58,539
We reviewed your case today.

68
00:08:59,481 --> 00:09:04,002
And I must say there was great
disappointment on the review committee.

69
00:09:32,566 --> 00:09:33,577
Come on.

70
00:09:34,804 --> 00:09:37,524
We gotta get you processed.
It'll take an hour or so.

71
00:09:37,684 --> 00:09:39,567
Bureaucracy must be served.

72
00:09:40,444 --> 00:09:43,885
But if you're lucky,
you'll get home by dinner time. Colonel.

73
00:09:45,852 --> 00:09:47,293
Come on.

74
00:09:47,771 --> 00:09:50,431
I'm not gonna hold
this door open forever.

75
